
sizeof(3)            LPC LIBRARY FUNCTIONS              sizeof(3)

NAME
     sizeof() - return the number of elements in an array or map-
     ping

SYNOPSIS
     int sizeof(mixed var);

DESCRIPTION
     Return the number of elements in an array or mapping  'var'.
     If `var' is not an array or a mapping, then '0' is returned.

SEE ALSO
     allocate(3).


